<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT53">
<l>kallā tavarilaṅkai kaṭṭaḻitta kākuttaṉ</l>
<l>ṉallā loruteyvam yāṉilēṉ pollāta</l>
<l>tēvarai tēvaral lārai tiruvillāt</l>
<l>tēvarait tēṟalmiṉ tēvu.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I do not have a god other than Kākutstha</l>
<l>who ruined the might of Laṅkā of the ignorant people.</l>
<l>Do not accept evil gods, those that are not gods,</l>
<l>[and] gods that have no holiness/Śrī as [being] divine.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
